---
title: Steak and Nectarine Salad with Spring Mix, Pecans, and Feta Cheese
description: This juicy steak salad comes together faster than you can say medium-rare. After you’ve sizzled the sirloin and quickly seared the nectarines, the work is practically done. The only thing that would make it simpler is if it assembled itself on top of the vinaigrette-dressed mixed greens on the plate (stay tuned for that feature).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/20-minute-steak-and-nectarine-salad-6fd3a943.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/20-minute-steak-and-nectarine-salad-a037714b.pdf
